{"tid":736674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[redvelvet]今日同wendy去釣魚同班mk決鬥...18+","createTime":"2018-07-10T11:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T13:41:19.000Z","uid":52073,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"141ea651ece2214ad6ba8d2e95741e31a47ebadd","tid":736674,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"今日天氣咁好就打算同wendy出去享受釣魚樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到個場已經有好多人係到釣緊 咁我就是但搵個位同wendy一齊坐係到一邊吹水一邊野餐一邊釣魚 好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n釣魚絕大部份時間都係等 見冇乜野做我咪企起身跳下ddu du ddu du順便消化下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhit you with that ddudu ddudu du....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\noh yeah...oh yeah....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跳跳下突然有2條mk仔走出黎兇鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =我     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =mk1    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =mk2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :咁撚夠薑敢係到跳bp?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你乜水?呢到唔跳得bp?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :咁串?敢唔敢係到即場battle?輸左既就躝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我就同佢地battle 內容係2人一隊每隊唱跳2首歌睇邊一邊勁d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為要評判所以就求奇班妹下妹下既廢老黎做評判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我想係wendy面前威番次(平時得夜晚先有得威一陣...90秒左右) 所以就叫wendy唔洗出戰我一個就夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時我成日睇上youtube睇fancam玩jer仔 基本上已經熟哂 我輸既可能性係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果2條mk隻1個揀左twice既heart shaker另一個就揀左TT(我笑左 TT都敢拎出黎跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n而我呢d badboy就緊係跳badboy同as if it's your last<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班mk仔其實都幾勁....一般人都應該贏唔到佢地,明顯有練過 不過好可惜對手係我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n點知跳完後班廢老竟然評班mk仔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一問先知 原來班廢老都係twice粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始我就已經中左計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我火到即刻衝上去打鳩班人 仲比班人一腳踢左落海浸暈左T T 最後要wendy救番我上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日好開心 我愛wendy!!❤"},{"pid":"5a0c4df5db8a9e59b5cd11e4757fecf8ef4fb054","tid":736674,"uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/195309_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F195309_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=742870f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsorry wendy 我又輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ccd30b75ad68b2a28668f707888cc13ebb6c82","tid":736674,"uid":52073,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"情境圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/195413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F195413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fd3d89b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60a990a07616258f9d3fef0ae4ac3d0d15830fcd","tid":736674,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"wendy有冇幫你打柒佢地？"},{"pid":"da4e7f8aca2139411413723c12da92f9cad0087a","tid":736674,"uid":115441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"成日比mk打，你都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ce8ca3c884e1f46e9c85fbbfec4920fde768b7","tid":736674,"uid":12308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"452217d44a2679c74af6b31f20070f6150384964","tid":736674,"uid":60982,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da4e7f8aca2139411413723c12da92f9cad0087a","tid":736674,"uid":115441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"成日比mk打，你都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"哂咁多時間打成篇垃圾仲慘啦"},{"pid":"61cec5ad78dd498a0f83451e39b08d3e987a2f02","tid":736674,"uid":52073,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"60a990a07616258f9d3fef0ae4ac3d0d15830fcd","tid":736674,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"wendy有冇幫你打柒佢地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"我地中伏在先冇計 不過wendy應該可以打死佢地<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/195632_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%